{"tid":1693792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人]   朋友失蹤","createTime":"2019-11-04T21:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:54:47.000Z","uid":307195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c59a4efde0d30d25d1fb9b31497aba516dcc7791","tid":1693792,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:24:53.000Z","msg":"佢大概喺02:45左右喺紅磡上左N121巴士<br />\n<br />\n佢屋企本身住土瓜灣 <br />\n正常返屋企20分鐘左右<br />\n<br />\n加上佢平時返到屋企都會講聲<br />\nWts灰雙剔 電話打得通但冇人聽<br />\n<br />\n暫時未聯絡到屋企人 <br />\n仲未知佢返咗屋企未<br />\n<br />\n160cm左右高 身型偏瘦 <br />\n黑色長頭髮 當時應該有孭書包<br />\n<br />\n有冇人喺N121巴士 / 土瓜灣附近見過類似特徵嘅女仔"},{"pid":"f05a9eae9c0b7aed3ec4863824269b498e50f50a","tid":1693792,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:25:40.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7b77d24b1c4acb8feee4381d546eaa96e7c9ab","tid":1693792,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:28:01.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6bce6a41bc7555c41333289d98b4a961217935","tid":1693792,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:29:01.000Z","msg":"已經過左3個鐘都完全聯絡唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656cbcb982aca96f7d47911be5a3907bc2fa03ed","tid":1693792,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:29:29.000Z","msg":"女仔黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c2ceaf99cd7a6826a8d0a5151855cebf74293a","tid":1693792,"uid":333312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:33:51.000Z","msg":"今晚嘅事？"},{"pid":"71982c61f75540bc48d6854a9b3cd020e2ac766b","tid":1693792,"uid":325465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T21:34:50.000Z","msg":"可能訓咗姐"},{"pid":"d7a1d2c80703228a0b68a6d9d697a3a41e930206","tid":1693792,"uid"